#3400
The Hall of Judgement~
   You step forth from beyond the veil and into the realm of Kelemvor.  You are
neither dead nor alive, and your presence here at the Hall of Judgement, given
that fact, means that you must go forth into the Realms, and leave this place of
stasis.  A ghostly being, a herald of some sort, urges you north through a set
of black, wrought-iron gates.  A voice speaks to your mind telling you to use
the @Ynewbie@n command if you need any help at any time.  If you are completely
new to muds please go east by typing @Yeast@n to begin the beginners lessons.  
