#3402
Choose Your Alignment~
   Here Kelemvor's servants urge you to select an alignment.  This should be an
easy choice for most spirits, as they each have their own personalities from the
beginning.  However each spirit has the choice to alter that personality before
they are born on Faerun.  TO change your alignment you may use @Ysetalign@n
<alignment>.  Your alignment is one of good, neutral or evil.  To set your
ethos, use @Ysetethos@n <ethos> Your ethos is one of lawful, nuetral or chaotic.
Your full alignment is your ethos followed by your alignment.  So lawful good
for example.  Your alignment will determine what equipment you can use, what
classes you can choose, and other aspects of being in the world of Faerun.  You
are urged to go north once you have chosen your alignment and ethos.  
