#3407
Beginner's Lesson 2 - Looking~
   You wil undoubtedly want to get greater detail on things throughout the game,
and one of the ways you can do this is by looking at them.  To look in the room
you are in simply type @Ylook@n.  To look at another player or a monster
(otherwise known as mob) type @Ylook @Y<name @Yor @Ydescription>@n To look at an
object type @Ylook @Y<object @Ydescription @Ykeyword>@n.  You can test this out
by typing @Ylook@n, @Ylook @Yself@n, and @Ylook @Ymap@n to look at the map in
your inventory.  
